# EdgeX API V2 Interface List

## Overview

This document outlines all V2 API endpoints for EdgeX HTTP Gateway, organized by service modules.

---

## I. Public API

### 1. Metadata Service

| SDK Method | API Path | Description |
|---------|---------|------|
| `GetServerTime` | `GET /api/v2/public/meta/getServerTime` | Get server time |
| `GetMetaData` | `GET /api/v2/public/meta/getMetaData` | Get global metadata (coin list, contract list, multi-chain config, etc.) |

### 2. Quote Service

| SDK Method | API Path | Description |
|---------|---------|------|
| `GetDepth` | `GET /api/v2/public/quote/getDepth` | Query order book depth |
| `GetKline` | `GET /api/v2/public/quote/getKline` | Query K-line data |
| `GetTicker` | `GET /api/v2/public/quote/getTicker` | Query 24-hour ticker |
| `GetTickerSummary` | `GET /api/v2/public/quote/getTicketSummary` | Get ticker summary |

### 3. Funding Rate Service

| SDK Method | API Path | Description |
|---------|---------|------|
| `GetLatestFundingRate` | `GET /api/v2/public/funding/getLatestFundingRate` | Query latest funding rate by contract ID |
| `GetFundingRatePage` | `GET /api/v2/public/funding/getFundingRatePage` | Query funding rate history by contract ID (paginated) |

---

## II. Private API (Authentication Required)

