| SDK Method | API Path | Description |
|---------|---------|------|
| `GetAccountAsset` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getAccountAsset` | Get account asset |
| `GetAccountPositions` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getAccountAsset` | Get account positions (extracted from asset response) |
| `GetPositionByContractID` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getPositionByContractId` | Get position by contract ID |
| `GetPositionTransactionPage` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getPositionTransactionPage` | Get position transaction records (paginated) |
| `GetPositionTransactionByID` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getPositionTransactionById` | Batch get position transactions by IDs |
| `GetPositionTermPage` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getPositionTermPage` | Get position term records (paginated) |
| `GetPositionOrders` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getPositionOrders` | **[V2 New]** Get historical orders by position term |
| `GetCollateralByCoinID` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getCollateralByCoinId` | Get collateral info by coin ID |
| `GetCollateralTransactionPage` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getCollateralTransactionPage` | Get collateral transaction records (paginated) |
| `GetCollateralTransactionByID` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getCollateralTransactionById` | Batch get collateral transactions by IDs |
| `GetAccountByID` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getAccountById` | Get account by ID |
| `GetAccountDeleverageLight` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getAccountDeleverageLight` | Get account ADL indicator |
| `GetAccountAssetSnapshotPage` | `GET /api/v2/private/account/getAccountAssetSnapshotPage` | Get account asset snapshots (paginated) |
| `UpdateLeverageSetting` | `POST /api/v2/private/account/updateLeverageSetting` | **[V2 New]** Update leverage setting |

