|---------|---------|------|
| `GetAllOrdersPage` | `GET /api/v2/private/assets/getAllOrdersPage` | Query all deposit/withdrawal order records (paginated) |
| `GetNormalWithdrawById` | `GET /api/v2/private/assets/getNormalWithdrawById` | Get normal withdrawal order by ID |
| `GetNormalWithdrawableAmount` | `GET /api/v2/private/assets/getNormalWithdrawableAmount` | Get normal withdrawable amount |
