| `CreateCrossWithdraw` | `POST /api/v2/private/assets/createCrossWithdraw` | Create cross-chain withdrawal order |
| `GetCoinRate` | `GET /api/v2/private/assets/getCoinRate` | Get coin exchange rate |
| `GetFastWithdrawById` | `GET /api/v2/private/assets/getFastWithdrawById` | Get fast withdrawal order by ID |
| `GetFastWithdrawSignInfo` | `GET /api/v2/private/assets/getFastWithdrawSignInfo` | Get fast withdrawal signature info |

### 3. Order Service

