| `GetHistoryOrderPage` | `GET /api/v2/private/order/getHistoryOrderPage` | Get historical orders (paginated, GET method) |
| `GetHistoryOrderPagePost` | `POST /api/v2/private/order/getHistoryOrderPage` | **[V2 New]** Get historical orders (paginated, POST method) |
| `GetOrderFillTransactions` | `GET /api/v2/private/order/getHistoryOrderFillTransactionPage` | Get historical order fill transactions (paginated) |

### 4. Transfer Service

| SDK Method | API Path | Description |
|---------|---------|------|
| `CreateTransferOut` | `POST /api/v2/private/transfer/createTransferOut` | Create transfer out order (auto L2 signature) |
| `GetTransferOutById` | `GET /api/v2/private/transfer/getTransferOutById` | Get transfer out order by ID |
| `GetTransferOutAvailableAmount` | `GET /api/v2/private/transfer/getTransferOutAvailableAmount` | Get available transfer out amount |
| `GetTransferInById` | `GET /api/v2/private/transfer/getTransferInById` | Get transfer in order by ID |

